<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer13789155463216401276"><i>Sir Ernst Hans Josef Gombrich</i>, OM, CBE (30 March 1909 – 3 November 2001) was an Austrian-born art historian, who spent most of his working life in the United Kingdom.<br/><br/></span>

